Interface MessageType

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
MessageTypeAdapter
public interface MessageType
extends java.lang.Cloneable

A read only interface to class MessageTypeImpl, which represents an HL7 v3 message type metadata.
